    "body": "Isn't ''**any** message\" too strong (instead of \"at least one message\"), especially here but also above?  `ProcessMessages`, `ProcessMessage` and `SendMessages`  can all return early. With `SendMessages`, it goes together with a disconnect, but for `ProcessMessage(s)` there are many other ways, so that in case of multiple messages not all might have been processed in this iteration of the loop.",
